main event: A disc-shaped object with blinking white lights was observed in Germansburg, Ohio, identified later as an aircraft with an aerial advertising sign.
interesting points: The observation was made outdoors near an airfield., The object had a flat appearance with a square window., It was reported that the object's lights turned off briefly for a second or two., The witness observed the phenomenon moving behind scattered clouds., The phenomenon was initially identified as an unidentified flying object, but later determined to be a Cessna 172 aircraft.
sighted object: a disc-shaped object with blinking white lights
witness description: Whitlines, an observer who reported seeing the phenomenon
